pageContext.claim: “Strongly Trending (Google) since immediately after the second debate is CAN I CHANGE MY VOTE? This refers changing it to me. The answer in most states is YES. Go do it. Most important Election of your life!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump’s confidence is misplaced. First off, it is not unusual for ‘can I change my vote’ to trend during an election season. Also, as Politifact reported, “only a handful of states allow ballots that have been returned to be called back prior to Election Day,” not most states as Trump claimed.
